uk.ac.aber.group14.model

Interface IWalk

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Walk

    public interface IWalk
    This interface is used to represent a walk This stores a collection of Location objects, a collection of IPointOfInterest objects, a String name, String short description, and String long description.
